quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,102,"Oyo niye Nyasaye wenyu omulesi, abulao nyasaye halali Ye, omulonji wa buli eshindu kho mumulame. Naye ni omulindi wabuli eshindu."
  6,103,"Tsimoni shitsiakhamulola tawe, naye atsilolanga. Naye niye omwihotselefu owuli nende amakhuwa koosi."
  6,104,"Toto bimalile okhubeetsela ebifune ebikhongo muno okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi. Kho ulia ufungula tsimoni yalola, nikhululwe omwene, ne ulia ulalola tawe nikhululwe omwene. Nasi shendi omulindi wenyu tawe (endisa omwikanyilisi)."
  6,105,"Ne endio nilwakhureranga tsimbia tsia tsinyaali, ne khobaboole mbu, “Okasomele (kano shikarula khu Nyasaye tawe)”, kho khukenoosilie abandu bamanya."
  6,106,"Londa kofimbulilungwa okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Abulao nyasaye ulamwa khubwatoto owulali Ye. Ne wire ehale nende abatsokaasinjia Nyasaye."
  6,107,"Ne Nyasaye yenyanga, shibakhabeele abamutsokasinjia tawe. Ne efwe shikhwakhukhola mbu obe omulenji wabu tawe. Nawe sholi omulindi wabu tawe."
  6,108,"Ne olanyeka balia ababalaamanga abalali Nyasaye tawe, baletsa banyeka Nyasaye khubufuru bwabu, nibalamanyile tawe. Endio nilwa khwaronela buli abandu ebikhole biabu. Mana ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi niwo wabalikalukha, naye alibaboolela akabakholanga."
  6,109,"Ne betsuba khu Nyasaye ebitsubo biabu bia amaani muno mbu; “Nibarererwa ebimanyisio, toto balabisuubila.” Boola mbu; “Toto ebimanyisio bili wa Nyasaye. Ne ni shina eshibamanyia mbu toto nibibetsera shibalabisuubila tawe?”"
  6,110,"Ne khwitsa okhukalukhania emioyo chiabu, nende tsimoni tsiabu shingala bakhaya okhukasuubila olwokhuranga. Ne khulabalekha mutsimbii tsiabu nibabeyabeyanga."